{"tid":1490344,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"普京大帝訪問法國，表明不欲俄羅斯發生類此黃背心示威 並會以法律保持莫斯科穩定","createTime":"2019-08-20T05:31:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T10:31:58.000Z","uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1cd009a82a4ae6c54091ef8c594684372f9974ae","tid":1490344,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T05:31:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1475599-20190820.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1475599-20190820.htm&d=QZ1X7Ww%2BB3pe%2FYPW%2Fe6VuTUBvjVF43IiJLn9vI4Fxnk%3D&h=f16620c7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1475599-20190820.htm&h=f3f5bb91\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1475599-20190820.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯總統普京到訪法國南部，與法國總統馬克龍會面。普京說，要防止在俄羅斯首都莫斯科，出現類似法國去年「黃背心」示威的抗議活動。<br />\n<br />\n莫斯科近日有大型示威，抗議當局拒絕反對派人士，參加市議會選舉。普京強烈批評這些抗議活動，表示不希望在俄羅斯首都發生這樣的事情。<br />\n<br />\n他又說，將盡一切努力，確保莫斯科的情況，維持在法律控制之內。"},{"pid":"26bd829be7cebe598a7c64310989476d4172e3ba","tid":1490344,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T05:34:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46ca4dbe99c39dc7eea62335aced7aa8eb31538b","tid":1490344,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T08:25:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8badc0758ccbe7c8dec8ff088b6d95d9fb4e2425","tid":1490344,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T08:25:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56c2eb7177a8225baa3606aa49147620b3be7414","tid":1490344,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T10:31:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gi